original_sql: SELECT MIN(l.l_shipmode) AS min_l_l_shipmode, AVG(l.l_partkey) AS avg_l_l_partkey, MIN(o.o_shippriority) AS min_o_o_shippriority, MAX(r.r_name) AS max_r_r_name, MIN(o.o_orderstatus) AS min_o_o_orderstatus FROM customer c, lineitem l, orders o, region r WHERE l.l_discount = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_partkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 50 AND (ps_availqty = 100 OR ps_availqty = 200) AND ps_comment LIKE 'Special%') AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT o_totalprice FROM orders UNION SELECT DISTINCT c_acctbal FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.18) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_custkey FROM customer UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000) AND l.l_discount = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_orderkey) FROM (SELECT l_orderkey, l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 10 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(s_suppkey) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey, s_nationkey FROM supplier JOIN nation ON s_nationkey = n_nationkey WHERE s_acctbal < 5000 ) AS t_5 GROUP BY s_nationkey ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT DISTINCT c_phone FROM customer UNION SELECT c_address FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 15) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_type FROM part JOIN supplier ON p_partkey = s_suppkey WHERE s_nationkey = 1 UNION SELECT p_retailprice, p_type FROM part JOIN lineitem ON p_partkey = l_partkey WHERE l_discount > 0.05 AND l_shipdate IN (SELECT l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_commitdate > '1996-01-01')) AS subq_7 GROUP BY p_type) AND r.r_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 800 INTERSECT SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'HOUSEHOLD')) AND o.o_orderkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 800 AND (s_nationkey = 4 OR s_nationkey = 8) AND 3+5=8 AND s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 2 AND 4*6=24)) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(s_acctbal) FROM (SELECT s_acctbal, s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey BETWEEN 1 AND 5 ) t GROUP BY s_nationkey ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'N%' AND o.o_totalprice > 56622.21100341347 AND c.c_custkey > 85271 AND l.l_partkey < 50647 AND o.o_orderkey < 4537761  LIMIT 100;

SELECT o.o_totalprice AS o_o_totalprice, COUNT(c.c_name) AS count_c_c_name, MIN(c.c_acctbal) AS min_c_c_acctbal, AVG(ps.ps_availqty) AS avg_ps_ps_availqty, SUM(o.o_orderkey) AS sum_o_o_orderkey FROM customer c, orders o, part p, partsupp ps WHERE EXISTS (SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT s_name, s_acctbal FROM supplier ) AS subq_1 UNION SELECT r_name FROM region) AND c.c_name IN (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' ) UNION SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1995-01-01' ) ORDER BY c_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_partkey = 9 ) AS subq_3 WHERE p_partkey > 8 ORDER BY p_partkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1997-06-30' UNION SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_retailprice > 250) AND p_size IN (SELECT p_size FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE ps_availqty > 150)) AND ps.ps_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT p_container FROM part ) t) AND p.p_size = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_address FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_address FROM supplier ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_orderpriority FROM (SELECT o_orderpriority, o_shippriority FROM orders ) AS subq_7 UNION SELECT p_mfgr FROM part) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT s_address FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_phone FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 10) AND o.o_orderkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_phone FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_phone FROM supplier ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_name FROM (SELECT p_name, p_retailprice FROM part ) AS subq_10 UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey AND c.c_acctbal < 6564.064854007466 AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#4%' AND ps.ps_availqty < 9424 AND o.o_orderkey = 5224614 AND ps.ps_supplycost < 901.2022349057664  GROUP BY o.o_totalprice LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(l.l_tax) AS count_l_l_tax, MAX(l.l_partkey) AS max_l_l_partkey, AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_c_c_acctbal, MIN(l.l_commitDATE) AS min_l_l_commitDATE, COUNT(s.s_phone) AS count_s_s_phone FROM customer c, lineitem l, nation n, orders o, supplier s WHERE n.n_nationkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT p_mfgr FROM part ) t) AND s.s_name IN (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_comment FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 3000) AND EXISTS (SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000 ) UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 5000 ) ORDER BY n_name) AND l.l_shipmode IN (SELECT l_shipmode FROM (SELECT l_shipmode, l_quantity FROM lineitem ) AS subq_4 UNION SELECT c_phone FROM customer) AND l.l_extendedprice > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n_nationkey) FROM nation JOIN (SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 3000 UNION ALL SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_comment LIKE '%excellent%') AS subq_5 ON nation.n_nationkey = subq_5.s_nationkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_clerk FROM (SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1995-06-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500) t GROUP BY o_clerk ORDER BY o_clerk) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT l_extendedprice FROM (SELECT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem UNION ALL SELECT o_totalprice FROM orders) AS u_7 JOIN partsupp ON u_7.l_extendedprice = ps_supplycost) AND o.o_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_orderkey) FROM lineitem WHERE l_partkey IN (SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_retailprice > 50 UNION SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_type = 'SMALL')) AND o.o_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_brand FROM part UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation ) t) AND c.c_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier JOIN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 60 UNION ALL SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 8) AS subq_10 ON supplier.s_suppkey = subq_10.ps_suppkey) AND l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey AND s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND l.l_tax <= 0.011999456372181961 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000014242%' AND c.c_acctbal = 2883.8766136284476 AND l.l_discount > 0.09017454621825115 AND l.l_linenumber < 5  LIMIT 10;

SELECT SUM(ps.ps_partkey) AS sum_ps_ps_partkey, AVG(c.c_custkey) AS avg_c_c_custkey, MIN(l.l_quantity) AS min_l_l_quantity, s.s_name AS s_s_name, AVG(l.l_orderkey) AS avg_l_l_orderkey FROM customer c, lineitem l, partsupp ps, supplier s WHERE l.l_suppkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem ) t) AND l.l_linenumber > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_name FROM part UNION ALL SELECT r_comment FROM region ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT p_type FROM part WHERE p_size > 20) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 10000) UNION ALL SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F')) t GROUP BY c_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT o_totalprice FROM orders UNION SELECT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem UNION SELECT l_extendedprice FROM (SELECT DISTINCT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem AS l1_5 WHERE l_shipdate > '1995-01-01') AS subq_5) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(l_quantity) FROM (SELECT l_quantity, l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate <= DATE '1995-12-31' ) t GROUP BY l_linestatus ORDER BY l_linestatus) AND c.c_custkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT c_custkey FROM customer UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1000) AND l.l_suppkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM (SELECT c_custkey, c_name FROM customer ) t) AND ps.ps_availqty = (SELECT (20 * 5) + COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM lineitem WHERE l_extendedprice IN (SELECT p_retailprice FROM part WHERE p_size < 15)) AND s.s_suppkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 1000) t JOIN nation ON n_nationkey = t.c_custkey) AND s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey AND ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey AND s.s_nationkey < 19 AND l.l_suppkey < 6670 AND l.l_orderkey <= 1944057 AND l.l_discount <= 0.08274340121023915 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'MACHINERY%'  GROUP BY s.s_name LIMIT 30;

SELECT MIN(l.l_orderkey) AS min_l_l_orderkey, MIN(l.l_tax) AS min_l_l_tax, COUNT(l.l_linestatus) AS count_l_l_linestatus, COUNT(p.p_name) AS count_p_p_name, COUNT(l.l_suppkey) AS count_l_l_suppkey FROM lineitem l, part p WHERE EXISTS (SELECT s_1.s_name FROM supplier s_1 WHERE s_1.s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_1.ps_suppkey FROM partsupp ps_1 WHERE ps_1.ps_supplycost > 200 UNION ALL SELECT ps2_1.ps_suppkey FROM partsupp ps2_1 WHERE ps2_1.ps_availqty < 30 GROUP BY ps2_1.ps_suppkey) AND s_1.s_acctbal < 1000) AND p.p_size > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1997-01-01' UNION ALL SELECT l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate < '1996-01-01') t JOIN supplier ON s_suppkey = t.o_orderkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 30 UNION SELECT p_partkey FROM part WHERE p_size > 15)) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_clerk FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate BETWEEN DATE '1997-01-01' AND DATE '1997-06-30' ) t GROUP BY o_clerk ORDER BY o_clerk) AND l.l_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_comment FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT ps_comment FROM partsupp ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT AVG(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_container FROM part WHERE p_size BETWEEN 5 AND 20 ) t GROUP BY p_container ORDER BY p_container) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_phone FROM customer UNION SELECT s_phone FROM (SELECT s_phone, COUNT(*) FROM supplier GROUP BY s_phone HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AS subq_7) AS t_7) AND l.l_linenumber = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 75 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 15) AS subq_8 ON part.p_partkey = subq_8.ps_partkey) AND l.l_returnflag IN (SELECT DISTINCT l_returnflag FROM (SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem UNION ALL SELECT o_orderstatus FROM orders) AS u_9 JOIN customer ON u_9.l_returnflag = c_phone) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' UNION SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity < 10 AND l_shipdate IN (SELECT l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1997-01-01')) AS subq_10 GROUP BY o_orderpriority) AND l.l_shipinstruct LIKE 'TAKE BACK RETURN%' AND l.l_linenumber > 1 AND p.p_partkey = 58547 AND l.l_receiptdate < '1996-10-15' AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'RAIL%'  LIMIT 10;

SELECT AVG(l.l_quantity) AS avg_l_l_quantity, SUM(ps.ps_partkey) AS sum_ps_ps_partkey, MIN(c.c_address) AS min_c_c_address, MAX(o.o_totalprice) AS max_o_o_totalprice, MAX(p.p_container) AS max_p_p_container FROM customer c, lineitem l, orders o, part p, partsupp ps WHERE EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, COUNT(*) FROM part GROUP BY p_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 4) AS subq_1) AS t_1) AND p.p_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_name) FROM (SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 8000 EXCEPT SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 1500 ) AS subquery_2) AND l.l_linestatus IN (SELECT DISTINCT l_linestatus FROM (SELECT l_linestatus FROM lineitem UNION ALL SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders) AS u_3 JOIN supplier ON u_3.l_linestatus = s_phone) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM (SELECT c_name, c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 4 ) AS subq_4 WHERE c_nationkey > 3 ORDER BY c_nationkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT MIN(p_size) FROM (SELECT p_size, p_container FROM part JOIN lineitem ON p_partkey = l_partkey WHERE p_retailprice < 50 ) AS t_5 GROUP BY p_container ORDER BY p_container) AND o.o_orderkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier JOIN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 60 UNION ALL SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 8) AS subq_6 ON supplier.s_suppkey = subq_6.ps_suppkey) AND ps.ps_suppkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 2000 AND (c_nationkey = 10 OR c_nationkey = 15) AND 3+4=7 AND c_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 3 AND 5*6=30)) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_partkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 100) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT DISTINCT c_phone FROM customer UNION SELECT c_address FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 15) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_partkey FROM part UNION SELECT ps_partkey FROM (SELECT ps_partkey, COUNT(*) FROM partsupp GROUP BY ps_partkey HAVING COUNT(*) > 3) AS subq_10) AS t_10) AND ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey AND ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey AND l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND p.p_name LIKE 'white papaya dim chartreuse pink%' AND c.c_custkey >= 84252 AND ps.ps_availqty = 158 AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '1-URGENT%' AND l.l_suppkey = 1297  LIMIT 10;

SELECT l.l_linestatus AS l_l_linestatus, COUNT(p.p_container) AS count_p_p_container, MIN(p.p_mfgr) AS min_p_p_mfgr, AVG(l.l_quantity) AS avg_l_l_quantity, r.r_regionkey AS r_r_regionkey FROM lineitem l, orders o, part p, region r WHERE EXISTS (SELECT p_mfgr FROM (SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1997-06-30' UNION SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount < 0.05) UNION ALL SELECT p_mfgr FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_returnflag = 'Y' UNION ALL SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_linestatus = 'F')) t GROUP BY p_mfgr) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_container FROM part UNION SELECT p_type FROM part WHERE p_size < 15) AND p.p_size = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey, p_retailprice FROM part WHERE p_container = 'SM BOX' ) t) AND r.r_name IN (SELECT DISTINCT r_name FROM region UNION SELECT p_type FROM part UNION SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_type FROM part AS p1_4 WHERE p_retailprice < 50) AS subq_4) AND l.l_discount = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM (SELECT l_linenumber FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 20 UNION ALL SELECT o_shippriority FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 500) t JOIN part ON p_partkey = t.l_linenumber) AND r.r_comment IN (SELECT r_comment FROM (SELECT r_comment, r_regionkey FROM region ) AS subq_6 UNION SELECT l_comment FROM lineitem) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'P' UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_orderkey) FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipmode = 'MAIL' UNION ALL SELECT 0 FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 1) AND o.o_orderkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderdate FROM orders ) t) AND l.l_linestatus IN (SELECT DISTINCT l_linestatus FROM (SELECT l_linestatus FROM lineitem UNION ALL SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders) AS u_9 JOIN supplier ON u_9.l_linestatus = s_phone) AND l.l_extendedprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 30 UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 200) AS partsupp_union_10 ON part.p_partkey = partsupp_union_10.ps_partkey) AND o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey AND l.l_suppkey = 4573 AND l.l_discount <= 0.044466884350784025 AND p.p_name LIKE 'thistle chartreuse olive cyan snow%' AND l.l_orderkey <= 4705447 AND p.p_retailprice >= 1096.525767805065  GROUP BY r.r_regionkey, l.l_linestatus LIMIT 100;

SELECT MAX(n.n_nationkey) AS max_n_n_nationkey, AVG(o.o_orderkey) AS avg_o_o_orderkey, MIN(ps.ps_partkey) AS min_ps_ps_partkey, n.n_nationkey AS n_n_nationkey, AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_p_p_retailprice FROM nation n, orders o, part p, partsupp ps, supplier s WHERE n.n_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n_nationkey) FROM nation JOIN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000 UNION ALL SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE') AS subq_1 ON nation.n_nationkey = subq_1.c_nationkey) AND s.s_acctbal = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_phone FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_phone FROM supplier ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_3.c_address FROM customer c_3 WHERE c_3.c_custkey IN (SELECT o_3.o_custkey FROM orders o_3 WHERE o_3.o_totalprice < 500 UNION ALL SELECT o2_3.o_custkey FROM orders o2_3 WHERE o2_3.o_orderdate < DATE '1994-12-31' GROUP BY o2_3.o_custkey) AND c_3.c_acctbal > 1000) AND p.p_brand IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_brand FROM part UNION SELECT DISTINCT s_address FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 5 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_comment FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 25) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_comment FROM customer UNION SELECT l_comment FROM lineitem UNION SELECT l_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT l_comment FROM lineitem AS l1_5 WHERE l_tax < 0.05) AS subq_5) AND ps.ps_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT r_regionkey) FROM (SELECT r_regionkey, r_name FROM region WHERE r_regionkey < 3 ) t) AND p.p_name IN (SELECT p_name FROM (SELECT p_name, p_retailprice FROM part ) AS subq_7 UNION SELECT n_name FROM nation) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_8.c_name FROM customer c_8 WHERE c_8.c_custkey IN (SELECT o_8.o_custkey FROM orders o_8 WHERE o_8.o_totalprice > 1000 UNION ALL SELECT o2_8.o_custkey FROM orders o2_8 WHERE o2_8.o_orderdate > DATE '1995-01-01' GROUP BY o2_8.o_custkey) AND c_8.c_acctbal < 0) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' UNION SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 10000) UNION ALL SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F')) t GROUP BY c_name) AND o.o_orderpriority IN (SELECT o_orderpriority FROM (SELECT o_orderpriority, o_shippriority FROM orders ) AS subq_10 UNION SELECT p_mfgr FROM part) AND ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey AND s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND n.n_regionkey <= 0 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'P%' AND p.p_name LIKE 'chartreuse bisque linen burnished cornflower%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#23%' AND s.s_acctbal <= 729.4994892758652  GROUP BY n.n_nationkey LIMIT 100;

SELECT SUM(c.c_nationkey) AS sum_c_c_nationkey, ps.ps_comment AS ps_ps_comment, MIN(o.o_shippriority) AS min_o_o_shippriority, MIN(ps.ps_partkey) AS min_ps_ps_partkey, MIN(p.p_retailprice) AS min_p_p_retailprice FROM customer c, orders o, part p, partsupp ps WHERE o.o_orderstatus IN (SELECT DISTINCT o_orderstatus FROM orders UNION SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 3000 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_extendedprice > 50) AND ps.ps_availqty = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_suppkey) FROM (SELECT ps_suppkey, ps_availqty FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' UNION SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 0)) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT c_phone FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 15000 ) UNION SELECT c_phone FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 15000 ) ORDER BY c_phone) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, COUNT(*) FROM part GROUP BY p_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 6) AS subq_5) AS t_5) AND p.p_retailprice IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_retailprice FROM (SELECT p_retailprice FROM part UNION ALL SELECT c_acctbal FROM customer) AS u_6 JOIN lineitem ON u_6.p_retailprice = l_tax) AND o.o_totalprice > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_orderpriority FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT p_container FROM part ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(s_suppkey) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey, s_nationkey FROM supplier JOIN nation ON s_nationkey = n_nationkey WHERE s_acctbal < 5000 ) AS t_8 GROUP BY s_nationkey ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND p.p_retailprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_discount) FROM lineitem JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice < 3000) AS order_union_9 ON lineitem.l_orderkey = order_union_9.o_orderkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM (SELECT s_name FROM supplier UNION ALL SELECT p_name FROM part) AS u_10 JOIN lineitem ON u_10.s_name = l_shipmode) AND o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey >= 5491 AND p.p_name LIKE 'lemon orchid misty cyan linen%' AND c.c_custkey >= 92042 AND p.p_container LIKE 'SM PKG%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#31%'  GROUP BY ps.ps_comment LIMIT 100;

SELECT ps.ps_partkey AS ps_ps_partkey, AVG(l.l_tax) AS avg_l_l_tax, SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS sum_c_c_acctbal, l.l_tax AS l_l_tax, COUNT(l.l_discount) AS count_l_l_discount FROM customer c, lineitem l, part p, partsupp ps WHERE p.p_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_returnflag) FROM lineitem JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F') AS order_union_1 ON lineitem.l_orderkey = order_union_1.o_orderkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT n_name FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 5000
